These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, sudoku
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Hobby   | camping  | sudoku |
| Flower     | iris | tulip  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, montecristo
City: berlin, new-york
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Cigar    | game      | montecristo         |
| City   | berlin | new-york |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, musical
2 different games are played: bridge, scrabble
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | animation   |
| Game       | scrabble  | bridge |

 #################################

 
